const GLOBALCONSTANT = {
        //Regular Expression
        GET_URL : /(https?:\/\/[^\s]+)/g,
        GET_TEXT : /`(.*?)`/,

        CONTACT: "Contact the developer ",
        TERMS : "Terms of service ",
        CANCEL:"Cancel ",
        TRY:"Try it out ",
        PARAMETERS:"Parameters ",
        NAME:"Name ",
        DESCRIPTION:"Description ",
        REQUIRED:"* required ",
        PARAMETER_CONTENT_TYPE:"Parameter content type ",
        RESPONSE_CONTENT_TYPE:"Response content type ",
        CODE:"Code ",
        RESPONSE:"Response ",
        SELECTEDRESPONSE:"application/xml",


        METHOD0:0,
        DATA0:0,
        TAGS:0,
        PARAM0:0,
        METHOD1:1,
        DATA1:1,
        ISSTRING:"string",

        POST:"post", 
        PUT:"put",
        GET:"get",
        DELETE:"delete ",

        BODY:"body",

        STRING:"string",
        INTEGER:"integer",
        FILE:"file",
    }
